    "Name": "Grand Dragon",
    "Details": "This Grand Dragon 1G model, was the custom 'Mech of Team Banzai MechWarrior Douglas Running-Elk. Simply known as the <b>Douglas</b>, Running-Elk preferred not to run at high temps and had the PPC removed and replaced by an AC/5. The LRM10 was downgraded to an LRM5 model and lastly, all but one Medium Laser was removed and an SRM6 placed in the left arm.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Stable</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>",
